text: Meng Qiang (born 3 July 1987) is a Chinese Greco-Roman wrestler. He competed in the 130 kg event at the 2016 Summer Olympics and was eliminated in the round of 16 by Bashir Babajanzadeh, from Iran.Men's Greco-Roman 130 kg 1/8 Final.
